body:
### Welcome to cmdline on github.io!
We don't do much 'round these parts. But at least this page gets updated from time to time... Kinda

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```


### Rather Drive Stick?
That's what she said....

### Support or Contact
irc://irc.thinstack.net/cmdline still works... probably. But it's probably better just to google for the email of one of the creators!
